Class QueryPlanner

java.lang.Object

public class QueryPlanner
extends java.lang.Object

Best on term preciousness, optional and must conditions the execution is sequenced. In each step one or more words gets matched. Precious must words executed first. In all downlevel processing, proper filteration is applied to eliminate unnecessary volume.
